en_327176_0	Appreciative of their years of service to the Army, Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake, Commander of the Army during 18-19 invited a group of 21 Regimental Sergeant Majors (RSMs), about to go on retirement to his office and lauded their exemplary services.
en_327176_1	During those brief meetings on both days, the Commander inquired into their past experiences and how the future would hold for them upon retirement.
en_327176_2	After extending his warm wishes, the Commander presented certificates of appreciation to all 21 RSMs.
en_327176_3	Brigadier Jayanath Jayaweera, Director Personnel Administration and the RSM at the Army Headquarters Battalion were present during those two brief meets at the Army Headquarters.
